title: 827. Rookies & Second-Year Players to Buy in the AFC & NFC South
itunes:title: 827. Rookies & Second-Year Players to Buy in the AFC & NFC South
description:
Daniel Jeremiah is back with a new episode of Move the Sticks and is joined by NFL Media's Lance Zierlein. To start off, the guys each give a rookie and second-year player they'd buy from the AFC South teams. Next, the pair react to the news of Buccaneers tight end Rob Gronkowski retiring. Then for the rest of the show, the duo each give a rookie and second-year player they'd buy from the NFC South teams.


Move the Sticks is a part of the NFL Podcasts Network.

See omnystudio.com/listener for privacy information.
